<title>重大突破！四川发现特大金矿</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4%EF%BC%81%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E7%89%B9%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%91%E7%9F%BF</link>
